These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-1::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, 7up, sprite
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: rowing, sailing, cricket
1. the person who's sport is sailing is in the middle##1
2. the person drinking sprite is the person who's sport is cricket##1
3. the person drinking iced-tea is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2    |    3    |
| Beverage   | iced-tea | 7up | sprite   |
| Sport      | rowing    | sailing  | cricket |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-2::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: sprite, coffee, soy-milk
There are 3 different nationalities: pakistani, german, turkish
1. the pakistani is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
2. the german is on the far left##1
3. the german is the person drinking coffee##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3     |
| Beverage      | coffee | sprite     | soy-milk      |
| Nationality   | german | pakistani | turkish |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-3::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: sprite, cola, hot-chocolate
There 3 different types of food: cabbage, cucumber, mango
1. the person drinking cola is on the right of the person eating cucumber##1
2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person eating mango##1
3. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the person eating cucumber##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2    |     3     |
| Beverage   | sprite | hot-chocolate  | cola       |
| Food       | cabbage     | cucumber | mango |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-4::.
There 3 different types of food: pumpkin, papaya, lime
The people have 3 different hobbies: magic-tricks, writing, camping
1. the person eating papaya is on the right of the person who's hobby is camping##1
2. the person eating pumpkin is on the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
3. the person who's hobby is camping is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2      |      3      |
| Food    | lime    | papaya     | pumpkin |
| Hobby   | camping | magic-tricks | writing     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-5::.
3 different pets are kept: cat, hamster, ferret
The people use 3 different means of transport: taxi, roller, bike
1. the person driving the roller is the owner of the ferret##1
2. the person driving the roller is on the right of the owner of the cat##1
3. the owner of the ferret is on the right of the person driving the taxi##1
4. the owner of the cat is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |    3     |
| Pet         | hamster | cat     | ferret |
| Transport   | bike        | taxi | roller    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-6::.
There 3 different types of food: eggplant, cranberry, banana
The people use 3 different means of transport: snowmobile, airplane, trike
1. the person eating eggplant is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
2. the person eating cranberry is on the right of the person driving the airplane##1
3. the person eating banana is the person driving the snowmobile##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2     |   3   |
| Food        | banana | eggplant      | cranberry  |
| Transport   | snowmobile       | airplane | trike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-7::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: ambient, country, blues
3 different pets are kept: horse, hamster, lizard
1. the fan of blues is on the left of the fan of ambient##1
2. the fan of country is the owner of the hamster##1
3. the owner of the horse is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |   3    |
| Music-Genre   | blues      | ambient     | country    |
| Pet           | horse | lizard | hamster |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-8::.
