.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-9::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: board-games, traveling, magic-tricks
3 different pets are kept: lizard, dog, chinchilla
1. the owner of the lizard is the person who's hobby is traveling##1
2. the owner of the dog is on the far right##1
3. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2      |   3    |
| Hobby   | magic-tricks | traveling | board-games  |
| Pet     | chinchilla     | lizard      | dog |

