.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-10::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: fanta, iced-tea, coffee
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: spy, animation, musical
1. the person watching musical movies is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
2. the person watching musical movies is on the far right##1
3. the person watching spy movies is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |   3    |
| Beverage      | fanta   | iced-tea    | coffee    |
| Movie-Genre   | animation | spy | musical |

