There are 3 different nationalities: italian, french, nigerian
1. the fan of gospel is the italian##1
2. the italian is on the left of the fan of soul##1
3. the nigerian is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |   3   |
| Music-Genre   | ambient | gospel   | soul  |
| Nationality   | nigerian    | italian | french |

