.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-13::.
There 3 different types of food: strawberry, orange, kiwi
The people have 3 different jobs:  mechanic, fisherman, project-manager
1. the fisherman is on the right of the person eating strawberry##1
2. the person eating kiwi is in the middle##1
3. the mechanic is on the right of the person eating kiwi##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |       1       |     2      |     3      |
| Food   | strawberry     | kiwi   | orange     |
| Job    | project-manager | fisherman | mechanic |

