.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-14::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  manager, chef, doctor
3 different pets are kept: cat, frog, rabbit
1. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the doctor##1
2. the doctor is on the left of the chef##1
3. the chef is on the right of the owner of the cat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1     |       2        |      3      |
| Job   | manager    | doctor | chef |
| Pet   | rabbit | cat     | frog        |

