.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-15::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: water, coffee, fanta
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: r&b, techno, soul
1. the person drinking coffee is on the far right##1
2. the fan of soul is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
3. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the fan of techno##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |   2   |     3     |
| Beverage      | water  | fanta | coffee  |
| Music-Genre   | techno | soul   | r&b |

 #################################

 
