.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-17::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  dancer, analyst, engineer
There are 3 different nationalities: canadian, chinese, mexican
1. the mexican is on the far left##1
2. the dancer is on the far right##1
3. the canadian is the engineer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2       |     3     |
| Job           | analyst | engineer | dancer |
| Nationality   | mexican  | canadian      | chinese |

