.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-18::.
There 3 different types of food: banana, cauliflower, corn
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: rugby, water-polo, sailing
1. the person who's sport is sailing is on the right of the person who's sport is rugby##1
2. the person eating banana is the person who's sport is sailing##1
3. the person eating corn is on the right of the person eating cauliflower##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |    2     |       3       |
| Food    | cauliflower | corn   | banana        |
| Sport   | water-polo    | rugby | sailing |

