1. the fan of folk is on the left of the fan of techno##1
2. the person who's hobby is reading is the fan of techno##1
3. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the right of the person who's hobby is reading##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |   3    |
| Hobby         | card-games | reading | dancing |
| Music-Genre   | folk | techno     | funk  |

