.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-20::.
There 3 different types of food: lemon, peas, banana
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: basketball, sailing, cricket
1. the person who's sport is sailing is in the middle##1
2. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left of the person eating lemon##1
3. the person eating peas is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2       |    3    |
| Food    | banana | lemon       | peas  |
| Sport   | cricket  | sailing | basketball |

 